# Game play UI

When creating or editing `packages/client/src/games/**`:

1. Read [`.cursor/design/game-ui.md`](../design/game-ui.md).
2. Wrap the view in **`GameShell`** from `components/game-shell` — never a custom full-page background.
3. Use **`GamePlayHeader`** for title (top-left) + leave/restart; **`GameOverActions`** on terminal phase.
4. Put board/hand UI in **`.card`** sections; use theme tokens (`var(--bg-*)`, `var(--text-*)`), not hardcoded page gradients.
